PLT WELLNESS AND MOUNTAIN RESORT

VISION: A PRIORITY DESTINATION OF GUESTS AND VISITORS IN THE  REGION  AS A PLACE OF RELAXATION, TEAM BUILDING AND FAMILY GATHERING. 

MISSION :   TO PROVIDE A SPECTACULAR EXPERIENCE  TO GUESTS AND VISITORS AS A RESULT OF  QUALITY SERVICE  IN A SAFE, HAPPY, HEALTHY,  COMFORTABLE AND FRIENDLY ENVIRONMENT. 

Specifically, it aims to:

To give prompt and efficient service to our guests by responding to their immediate needs and welfare. 
To provide a safe and humane environment to our staff.
To provide a professional employee-employer relationship by adopting a culture of openness, teamwork, respect, commitment and dedication.
To train and develop our staff of having a well rounded personality to boost self confidence, high self esteem and become great servants.
To give a significant contribution to the tourism industry and to the community.
To provide an equitable return of investment to the owners of the resort.
To provide excellent service to the guests and visitors that inspires them to come over and over again.

- from mommy non

